---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="The Sunday Letter — AfterChildren"
  description="The Sunday Letter from AfterChildren — one essay every Sunday morning for parents whose children are grown. Launches once the first thousand readers arrive. Until then, the four founding manifesto essays are free on the site."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="page">
    <div class="sl-hero">
      <p class="sl-hero__eyebrow">The Sunday Letter</p>
      <h1 class="sl-hero__title">
        Coming soon.<br />
        <em>The essays are already here.</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="sl-hero__lede">
        The Sunday Letter is the weekly inbox version of this site — one long essay, every Sunday morning, no filler, no advertiser noise. It launches once the first thousand readers have arrived. Until then, the four founding manifesto essays are free to read at the link below, and we are shipping the rest of the cornerstone content first.
      </p>
      <p class="sl-hero__lede">
        We could send a newsletter to twelve people right now. We have chosen not to. The Sunday Letter exists to be the most useful single email a parent in their second half gets each week — and that promise is harder to keep when the list is too small for the rhythm to be worth the discipline. We will switch it on when it is worth your attention.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT'S ALREADY HERE -->
  <section class="page">
    <div class="sl-samples">
      <p class="sl-samples__eyebrow">Already free, already live</p>
      <h2 class="sl-samples__title">The four founding manifesto essays.</h2>
      <p class="sl-samples__intro">
        These are the cornerstone pieces — the four essays that explain what this whole project is, and is not. They are the voice you would get every Sunday once the letter ships. Read any of them and you will know whether the eventual Sunday Letter is for you.
      </p>
      <div class="sl-samples__list">
        <a href="/manifesto" class="sl-sample">
          <span class="sl-sample__tag">Pinned</span>
          <h3 class="sl-sample__title">The AfterChildren Manifesto</h3>
          <p class="sl-sample__excerpt">Why this site exists, what it stands for, what it refuses to say.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/manifestos/you-raised-them-now-build-yourself" class="sl-sample">
          <span class="sl-sample__tag">14 min read</span>
          <h3 class="sl-sample__title">You Raised Them. Now Build Yourself.</h3>
          <p class="sl-sample__excerpt">The five-sovereignty framework underneath the entire site.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/manifestos/adult-children-not-retirement-plan" class="sl-sample">
          <span class="sl-sample__tag">15 min read</span>
          <h3 class="sl-sample__title">The Hardest Truth: Your Adult Children Are Not Your Retirement Plan</h3>
          <p class="sl-sample__excerpt">The quiet assumption baked into millions of retirement plans, and the math underneath why it fails.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/manifestos/moving-in-with-kids-fails" class="sl-sample">
          <span class="sl-sample__tag">14 min read</span>
          <h3 class="sl-sample__title">Why Moving In With Your Kids Almost Always Fails</h3>
          <p class="sl-sample__excerpt">The 70% failure rate nobody warned you about, the three patterns where it works, and the alternative.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT THE LETTER WILL BE -->
  <section class="page">
    <div class="sl-whatyouget">
      <p class="sl-whatyouget__eyebrow">What it will be, when it ships</p>
      <h2 class="sl-whatyouget__title">The Sunday Letter, defined.</h2>
      <div class="sl-whatyouget__grid">
        <div class="sl-feature">
          <h3 class="sl-feature__title">One essay, 1,500 to 3,500 words</h3>
          <p class="sl-feature__desc">Not a roundup. Not a digest. Not "here are 14 articles you should read." One piece, written deliberately, on a single question that matters in the second half of life. If there is nothing useful to say in a given week, the week gets skipped. We do not pad.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sl-feature">
          <h3 class="sl-feature__title">No advertising in the body</h3>
          <p class="sl-feature__desc">There may eventually be a small sponsor line at the top or bottom — clearly labeled, never in the middle of the essay, never affecting the editorial. The essay you are reading is the essay we wrote. Nobody paid to be in it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sl-feature">
          <h3 class="sl-feature__title">No pity. No hedging.</h3>
          <p class="sl-feature__desc">The tone of most over-55 newsletters is condescending, hedging, or therapeutic. This one will not be. We will treat the reader as an adult who can handle direct information about money, body, mind, legal, and living decisions, and who is tired of being told what they want to hear.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sl-feature">
          <h3 class="sl-feature__title">Unsubscribe in one click</h3>
          <p class="sl-feature__desc">When it ships: every email will have a one-click unsubscribe link in the footer. No retention loop. No "we'll miss you" survey. If the letter is not for you, leave. We will not track you, sell your email, or use it for any purpose other than sending the letter.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BOOKMARK CTA -->
  <section class="page">
    <div class="sl-bookmark">
      <h2 class="sl-bookmark__title">Bookmark this page.</h2>
      <p class="sl-bookmark__lede">
        When the Sunday Letter goes live, this page becomes the place to subscribe. Until then, the site itself is the letter — read the manifesto, work through the five sovereignty pillars, and come back. The essays do not require an inbox.
      </p>
      <a href="/" class="sl-bookmark__cta">Back to the homepage <span class="sl-bookmark__arrow">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  /* HERO */
  .sl-hero {
    padding: var(--space-24) 0 var(--space-12);
    max-width: 44rem;
  }
  .sl-hero__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ember);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  .sl-hero__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, var(--text-4xl));
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 100;
  }
  .sl-hero__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ember);
  }
  .sl-hero__lede {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ash);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* SAMPLES */
  .sl-samples {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--stone);
  }
  .sl-samples__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ember);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .sl-samples__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 32rem;
  }
  .sl-samples__intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ash);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    max-width: 36rem;
  }
  .sl-samples__list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--stone);
  }
  .sl-sample {
    display: block;
    padding: var(--space-8) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--ink);
    transition: padding 0.3s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .sl-sample:hover {
    padding-left: var(--space-4);
  }
  .sl-sample__tag {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-3xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ember);
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  .sl-sample__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  .sl-sample__excerpt {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ash);
  }

  /* WHAT YOU GET */
  .sl-whatyouget {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--stone);
  }
  .sl-whatyouget__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ember);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .sl-whatyouget__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    max-width: 32rem;
  }
  .sl-whatyouget__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--stone);
    border: 1px solid var(--stone);
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .sl-whatyouget__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  .sl-feature {
    background: var(--bone);
    padding: var(--space-10) var(--space-8);
  }
  .sl-feature__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .sl-feature__desc {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ash);
  }

  /* BOOKMARK */
  .sl-bookmark {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0 var(--space-24);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--stone);
    max-width: 36rem;
  }
  .sl-bookmark__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .sl-bookmark__lede {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ash);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  .sl-bookmark__cta {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ember);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ember);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    transition: gap 0.25s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .sl-bookmark__cta:hover {
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }
  .sl-bookmark__arrow {
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.25s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .sl-bookmark__cta:hover .sl-bookmark__arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
</style>
